that wicked men do Load you with Contumelious <choice ana="illegible">
                     <sic>La*<normalised orig="guage" auto="true">gauge</normalised></sic>
                     <corr>Language</corr>
                  </choice>, and<lb/>
oppressive Fines and Mulcts, or do inflict on you Corporal Punishments<lb/>
