But what a <normalised orig="rejoycing" auto="true">rejoicing</normalised> is it, that by this very means, you are<lb/>
so particularly assured of a most glorious <normalised orig="Recompence" auto="true">Recompense</normalised>: Besides<lb/>
the inexpressible Consolation, God will secretly Communicate at<lb/>
