Evildoer, or as a <normalised orig="busie" auto="true">busy</normalised> Body in other <normalised orig="mens" auto="true">men's</normalised> Matters.</quote> These are the<lb/>
faults and Characters of Persecutors themselves, and for these<lb/>
things men ought to suffer. See that your Consciences be clear<lb/>
and well informed. Take care to understand the thing you contend<lb/>
for. Weigh your Opinions and your Practices in the <normalised orig="Ballance" auto="true">Balance</normalised><lb/>
of the Sanctuary. Be sure your cause be Good, and then if you are<lb/>
