with some pretence to palliate and gloss the Fact.<lb/>
But it is not enough that you have something to Plead and<lb/>
say in your own defence amongst men, unless it be what will be<lb/>
                  <lb/>
                  <fw type="pageNum" n="20">D2</fw>
                  <pb n="14"/>
                  <lb/>
warranted and approved by the judge of all, for if you could so<lb/>
