This seems not to have any of that Meekness, <normalised orig="Condescention" auto="true">Condescension</normalised>,<lb/>
and Forbearance our Religion <normalised orig="doth" auto="true">does</normalised> so expressly and so vehemently<lb/>
<normalised orig="inforce" auto="true">enforce</normalised>.<lb/>
Nay your addicting your selves to such Courses will <normalised orig="indanger" auto="true">endanger</normalised><lb/>
