the Honour of being caressed by great men, will <normalised orig="indanger" auto="true">endanger</normalised> to<lb/>
<normalised orig="qualifie" auto="true">qualify</normalised> them to undertake with unconcernedness and Triumph<lb/>
the most barbarous and inhumane Persecutions imaginable.<lb/>
